msgid "Accredible groups were successfully updated."
msgstr "Accredible समूह सफलतापूर्वक अपडेट किए गए।"

#: apps/badges/admin_forms.py
msgid "You can't provide an API key for a configured organization."
msgstr "आप कॉन्फ़िगर किए गए संगठन के लिए API कुंजी प्रदान नहीं कर सकते।"

